{
  "chapter": 46,
  "chapter_summary": "郭少峰身中巨毒二十余年，芮玮以金针过穴法配解毒丸将其治愈。郭少峰感恩戴德，欲报恩杀人。芮玮掏出匕首请求郭少峰刺瞎自己左眼，代替大师伯刘忠柱偿还当年误伤之仇。郭少峰坚决拒绝，以死相胁阻止芮玮自伤，最终答应与刘忠柱一笔勾消恩怨。芮玮离开不归谷，在谷口遇到苦等两日两夜的叶青和已治愈的简怀萱。简怀萱讲述天池府惨变——简大哥受叶士谋魔心眼术控制，杀母弑弟，又以邪术令简怀萱失去心智。叶青告知林琼菊被叶士谋判处死刑，下落不明。芮玮怒闯叶士谋住处，误入一间闺房，撞见一位神秘花衣女子。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你真能帮我解去二十多年来的痛苦枷锁？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "小弟深晓各种毒物的毒性，要解巨毒并不为难。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谢天谢地，想不到少峰也将有不痛苦的一天……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们何时开始？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "事不宜迟，小弟这就替你着手除毒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "待我先把归真的尸体埋葬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小兄弟，我老哥还有这么一天，可见苍天悯人，自今后老哥也不柝杀世人了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "兄弟，你把我从地狱救转，这种恩惠如何能报？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "你只要不杀好人，除暴安良，比再怎样谢我都好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你给我这把匕首做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "小弟有一事求你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "别说一事，就是十件事老哥无不从命。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "这件事怕你下不了手！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么事，要我杀人吗，哪一个？小兄弟认为该杀的人定然罪无可赦，我要下不了手，不得好死！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "赌什么咒，快快收回。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，你说到底要杀什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "你用匕首将我这只眼睛戙矮，快，我决不怪你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "为……为……什么……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "当年大师伯不知，无意伤了你的眼睛，使得你痛苦二十多年，这种仇恨你不能不报，但是我的大师伯他年纪老了，又死了爱妻，自居墓中伴着妻骨度日，他不能再接受你的报复，我年青劚壮，瞎了一只眼睛没什么要紧，长辈有劳，弟子服之，你就成全我这番心意吧！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "张玉珍是大师伯的师妰，他事先决不知你身中巨毒，更不知那巨毒是张玉珍害的，只因他路过碰到，见你要杀他师妰，焉能不伸之以援手呢？要是他知道你因毒性发作不能防守决不会出手凌厉一剑，事有那么凑巧，就那一剑竟将你眼睛戙矮了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玬",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "但这大错铸成，无法挺回，等大师伯知道其中原委悔之已晚，今日我来承当这罪过，你不要为难，有仇就报吧！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不！不！我怎能向恩重如山的小兄弟报这仇恨，你不要说了，我自会去找刘忠柱索还这笔仇恨，我不一定胜得了他，让我死在他的剑下好了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "你就不能成全我这番心意吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不行！不行！冤有头，债有主……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "你不忍下手，我自己来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你戮瞎眼睛，我就立时死在你的眼前。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你去吧，我答应此后与刘忠柱的仇恨一笔勾消！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "小弟仅代大师伯感谢你的大量，今后不知你当如何？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不久我就要离开此地，咱们日后江湖见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "那小弟告辞了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "魔鬼岛上不是个好地方，你办完事后速速离开。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "小弟知道，一当事完，立即离开。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小兄弟……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_shao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没事，没事，但望咱们再相见时不忘今日的情分……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出来啦，出来啦……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，大哥……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "妹妹，你的病好了吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我的病好了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "到底是个假大哥，行动不能太随便呀！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你……你……还是我的大哥……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "你站在这里做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "青姐带我来此……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "叶小姐，你好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "青姐说在这里可以等到大哥，她说你到谷中去，生死不知，放心不下，就来这里等啦，到今天已等了二天二夜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "既然等到了，我可以走了，你们好好谈谈。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "叶小姐，谢谢你……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不要叫我叶小姐好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "青儿……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，我可以这样叫你吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "可以，可以，只要你愿意这样叫我。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我求爹，爹就马上将萱妹治好了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我好像做了一个长长的的噩梦，噩梦醒来，人事全非……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "天池府现在怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "娘死了，二哥也死了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "谁杀死的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥杀的，大哥杀的！我亲眼看见他杀的……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "好狠的家伙！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "娘虽对大哥不好，大哥也不该这样狠心呀，不！从此我再也不认他大哥了，二哥无罪，他竟连他也杀了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "他的未婚妻呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不知道，刘姐姐本领大不会死的，那天我亲眼看见他杀死娘和二哥，娘和二哥就任他杀，也不知还手……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "当时我吓呆住了，模模糊糊地看到一个秀才向我走来，盯着我看，口中说：怀萱姑娘，你的心呢？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不知不觉应道：我的心？在哪里？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那位秀才说：你的心丢了……听到这话，脑中嗡的一响，就此失去知觉直到前两天才醒来。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "那位秀才是我爹爹，他重将你醒转，你不要再怪他好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "我不知道要不要怪他，青姐，你对我好，我很感激你！",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "林琼菊呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "告诉我，林琼菊在哪里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那…那天求爹治萱妹，爹说一命换一命，芮公子将你救活，爹只救他妹妹，算报答他的恩德，至于另一女子无故闯到魔鬼岛上，该处一死，以示告戒。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我急急求爹说她是你的妹妹，爹不答应说非处死不可，就是见到你也要处死，我怕你从不归谷出来碰到爹爹，所以等在这里，你……你快带萱妹走吧，船已备好……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "菊妹死了没有？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不晓得，当天就再没有看到她……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你到哪里去？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "找你爹爹去理论！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "啊！你来了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "对不起！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你忍心再抛弃我吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    }
